OL,3,CMore patients in NI treated in
OL,4,Chospital corridors than any other part
OL,5,Cof the UK
OL,7,FA new report by the Royal College of
OL,8,FEmergency Medicine (RCEM) has shown
OL,9,Fthat more patients in Northern Ireland
OL,10,Fare being treated in hospital
OL,11,Fcorridors than anywhere else in the UK.
OL,13,FIt comes as Emergency Departments
OL,14,Fstruggle to cope with demand amid a
OL,15,Fsurge in flu cases.
OL,17,FThe Vice President of the RCEM in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland has said the findings
OL,19,Fof the new report are "startling".
