OL,3,CMore patients in NI treated in
OL,4,Chospital corridors than any other part
OL,5,Cof the UK
OL,7,FThe report from the RCEM provides a
OL,8,Fstark picture of life in Emergency
OL,9,FDepartments across the UK from figures
OL,10,Frecorded in March.
OL,12,FDr Michael Perry told UTV: "It is much
OL,13,Fworse in Northern Ireland. Our figures
OL,14,Fare double that of England, double
OL,15,Fthat of Scotland, we're worse than
OL,16,FWales.
OL,18,F"I'm expecting to come in to a lot of
OL,19,Fpatients awaiting beds on the ward.
OL,20,FI'm expecting to come in to patients
OL,21,Fawaiting in cars and in corridors.
