OL,7,F"I'm expecting to drive in to work and
OL,8,Flook to my left and see ambulances
OL,9,Fparked outside the Emergency
OL,10,FDepartment, many of which contain
OL,11,Fpatients to be offloaded."
OL,13,FHealth trusts in Northern Ireland are
OL,14,Fnow asking those attending hospitals
OL,15,Fto wear masks. The Public Health
OL,16,FAgency has also re-issued a call for
OL,17,Fpeople to get vaccinated against the
OL,18,Fflu, in a bid to ease the strain.
