OL,7,FDr. Ultan Power, Professor of
OL,8,FMolecular Virology, Queen's University
OL,9,FBelfast said: 'The virus is likely to
OL,10,Fbe circulating for several weeks yet.
OL,12,F"It would be helpful to roll out that
OL,13,Fvaccine to as many people as we can in
OL,14,Fthe schools, and to try to encourage
OL,15,Fhealthcare workers to take up the
OL,16,Fvaccine as well.
OL,18,F"It won't necessarily eliminate, but
OL,19,Fit will help diminish the number of
OL,20,Fpeople that are getting seriously
OL,21,Faffected by infection."
