OL,3,CMore patients in NI treated in
OL,4,Chospital corridors than any other part
OL,5,Cof the UK
OL,7,FMore than 500 hospital beds are
OL,8,Fcurrently out of use because people
OL,9,Fwho are medically fit cannot be
OL,10,Fdischarged due to a lack of community
OL,11,Fcare.
OL,13,FDiane Dodds MLA, DUP Health Committee
OL,14,Fmember said: "That is like saying to
OL,15,Fthe health service that we will shut
OL,16,Fdown Altnagelvin, or we'll shut down
OL,17,Fthe Ulster Hospital.
OL,19,F"To expect the health service to work
OL,20,Ffor everyone with that amount of beds
OL,21,Fmissing. It just can't be done."
