OL,3,CMore patients in NI treated in
OL,4,Chospital corridors than any other part
OL,5,Cof the UK
OL,7,FThe study analysed five snapshots
OL,8,Ftaken from 165 A&E departments across
OL,9,Fthe UK in March 2025.
OL,11,FThe report found more than 10,000
OL,12,Fpeople were being treated in
OL,13,F"escalation areas", classed as any
OL,14,Farea not routinely used for care
OL,15,Fincluding corridors, waiting rooms,
OL,16,Fdoubled-up cubicles and ambulances.
